# Web3 Backend Integration Demo

This repository is a demo setup prepared for client collaboration, focusing on backend integration for decentralized trading platforms.

## 🔧 Tech Stack

- **Node.js / TypeScript** – Backend APIs
- **Ethers.js / Web3.js** – Blockchain interactions
- **TradingView Alerts** – Signal-based automation
- **The Graph** – On-chain data indexing
- **Redis & Caching** – Performance optimization
- **Supabase (optional)** – Auth and data handling

## 🧠 Key Features

- TradingView alert to Smart Contract execution
- DEX integration (e.g., Uniswap, GMX)
- JWT-secured APIs
- Modular and scalable architecture

## 📦 Status

This is a placeholder setup. Full codebase will be added upon project approval.

